snippet.title: Driving Homeicide Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer #1 for Driving Home-icide, a focused and humorous single-player driving experience as you, the self-driving AI, must deliver your increasingly inebriated and distracting owner for their night on the town. Survive the increasingly difficult levels as your owner ramps up their 'help' and deliver them home in once piece.

Features over 400 voice lines, keyboard and gamepad support, story mode and free-driving survival mode.

Demo:  https://chimeracoast.itch.io/drivinghomeicide
Wishlist:  https://store.steampowered.com/app/2720210/Driving_Homeicide/
